last_episode_to_air.name: High Octane Run
last_episode_to_air.overview: Contestants take on tough new challenges, a longer zip line, and a 40-foot volcano with a water slide to win prizes worth over $5,000.

name: Paradise Run
overview: Paradise Run puts teamwork to the test in a beautiful tropical setting. Each week, three teams of two compete in the ultimate vacation challenge!

episodes.name: Besties
episodes.overview: Three teams of best friends battle for first place as they dive deep for lost party treasures. Then, they have to dance their way across the resort to serve up some cool Hawaiian treats on the beach.

episodes.name: Splish-Splash and Dash
episodes.overview: After splish-splashing their way to the pool and tossing tubes to each other, three teams try to solve a very tricky tiki puzzle before running to the beach to put on some extra special Hula outfits.

episodes.name: Girl Power
episodes.overview: Three girl duos have to pedal hard to gather beach balls but the resort's waterfall almost sinks their boats. Then, before they can reach the finish line, more than one team gets stuck on the riddle.

episodes.name: Puzzled Tiki
episodes.overview: Teams battle it out in a race where teamwork and memorization are key. A detour could sink one team's chances at the waterfall while the others splash down the slide to get puzzled by an ancient tiki.

episodes.name: Dig, Slide and Toss
episodes.overview: After digging for Sand Dollars on the beach, three teams of siblings and besties hop their way across super slippery islands to toss some coconuts before scrambling to set up a very important cabana.

episodes.name: Panic Under the Falls
episodes.overview: As the teams speed across the resort, they discover it's hard to get an angry tiki in line and filling up a bucket under the raging waterfall proves no easy task.

episodes.name: Cabana-Rama Adventure
episodes.overview: Teams sprint to the pool to toss leis at each other and try not to wipe out on the slippery islands before going on a free-for-all scavenger hunt to build a very important cabana.

episodes.name: Hidden Zodiac
episodes.overview: Three teams order up some fun racing around a Hawaiian resort and flex their searching skills for animals hidden around the pool.

episodes.name: Where's My Charger
episodes.overview: Three teams dash across a Hawaiian resort, but some bad steering at one of the pedal boats could sink another's chances. Then, one team gets stuck on a very tricky grid at the bottom of the slide.

episodes.name: What a Mess
episodes.overview: It's BFFs vs. cousins vs. twins in a race around a Hawaiian resort that's anyone's game. The teams order up some fun in the lagoon, then Hula across the island to hunt for several lost items.

episodes.name: Riddle Me This
episodes.overview: Three teams toss giant rings overboard on a wet and wild adventure in Paradise where they must build a giant tiki and Hula their way through a scavenger hunt on a race to victory.

episodes.name: Hula What?
episodes.overview: BFF's rule in this super tight race around paradise where three teams must Hula their way over to the pool to find lost treasures.

episodes.name: Moving Statues
episodes.overview: Three teams scramble to find and match phrases on the floating bottles in the lagoon, then some get stumped by giant animal statues around the pool in a wild zodiac-themed challenge.

episodes.name: Raging Falls
episodes.overview: Three teams speed across the resort, discovering that it is hard to get an angry tiki in line and that it is not easy to fill a bucket under a raging waterfall.

episodes.name: Going Coconuts for Sand Dollars
episodes.overview: Digging up enough sand dollars is no easy task as three teams paddle across the lagoon, then try to set up a crazy cabana before tossing coconuts AND leis in a very slippery challenge.

episodes.name: Mix N Match
episodes.overview: Three teams of besties race to the finish line of a Hawaiian resort, matching phrases floating in the lagoon. But one team's momentum gets tripped up by a costly mistake.

episodes.name: Water Wonderland
episodes.overview: Teams scramble to check out of their hotel rooms, then get into their boats to do battle with a waterfall before using their spelling and swimming skills to make an island connection.

episodes.name: Are We There Yet?
episodes.overview: Racing to the number one spot, three teams each test their memory on a tricky slide and then brave the jungle to wake up a sleeping tiki. But one team gets waterlogged while fighting to hold the lead.

episodes.name: Puzzles in Paradise
episodes.overview: Three pairs of teammates scramble to match a funny set of Hula outfits. Then, they rush to the pool to toss tubes onto slippery islands before using their smarts to solve a very special puzzle.

episodes.name: What's Apple-Pine?
episodes.overview: Three teams rush to deliver everything but the kitchen sink, to hotel guests for a tip. Then, they race to the beach to start matching floating word pairs before a mad dash to the finish line.

episodes.name: It's All About the Thunder-man!
episodes.overview: In the second-season opener, cast members from "The Thundermans" team up with fans to throw fish and zip-line to a wedding.

episodes.name: NRDD Run for Charity
episodes.overview: Paradise Run welcomes the stars of Nicky, Ricky, Dicky & Dawn, as Lizzy Greene, Mace Coronel and Kyla-Drew Simmons take on a packed minivan, party pedal boats, and a giant ukulele!

episodes.name: Thundermans in Paradise
episodes.overview: The Thundermans are on Paradise Run! Kira Kosarin, Addison Riecke , and Ryan Newman pair up with their biggest superfans to zip into a 70's dance party with an appearance from Jack Griffo!

episodes.name: NRDD in the House
episodes.overview: Nicky, Ricky, Dicky & Dawn do Paradise Run! Stars of the hit show team up with their super fans and run to extinguish an unusual volcano, match mixed-up packages, and make a crazy lei.

episodes.name: A Nick Showdown in Paradise
episodes.overview: The stars of The Thundermans take on the stars of Nicky, Ricky, Dicky, & Dawn in this action-packed special episode. Plus, a special appearance from Jack Griffo!

episodes.name: Whose Underwear Is That?
episodes.overview: Three teams of best friends and siblings search for sunken treasure, run in frozen underwear and catch some flying fish.

episodes.name: I Scream for Ice Cream
episodes.overview: Teams of best friends battle cousins to become VIPs, make a massive waffle cone treat and tune up a giant ukulele.

episodes.name: Lava Reception
episodes.overview: A boiling volcano, epically lost phones, and mixed-up mail in the lagoon, challenge three teams of best friends in paradise.

episodes.name: Forgive You Not!
episodes.overview: In a Hawaiian Paradise, three teams of BFF's and siblings battle to save a family of turtles, sport a sumo-size sponge suit, and run to a very wet wedding.

episodes.name: Crazy Lei, Crazy Time
episodes.overview: Sisters compete against two BFF teams in an epic battle to rebuild a wobbly reef, shop for snorkel gear, and string a colorful lei by flying down a massive slide.

episodes.name: What's My Flavor?
episodes.overview: Two teams of best friends take on a brother-and-sister duo where they must rocket rainbow scoops, tune up a ukulele and dress to impress.

episodes.name: Something's Fishy
episodes.overview: Can you say Humuhumunukunukuapua'a? To win the run in Paradise, BFF and sister teams must name Hawaii's state fish and wear multiple pairs of frozen shorts.

episodes.name: The Butt Squeeze
episodes.overview: Three fierce teams battle each other in a tight race where they suit up in giant sponge suits to quash their beefs.

episodes.name: Zip, Launch & Fly
episodes.overview: Things fall apart in Paradise when a 12- year-old uncle and his 11-year-old nephew battle twins and a brother/sister team to save a wedding.

episodes.name: Paradise Express
episodes.overview: Three teams of children must cool down a volcano and find hidden cell phones to win a tropical vacation.

episodes.name: Skip, Drip & Zip
episodes.overview: A 12-year-old uncle and his 11-year-old nephew battle twins and a brother-and-sister team to save a wedding.

episodes.name: Salute Your Frozen Butt
episodes.overview: Teams of best friends battle racing twins as they search for sunken secrets in the lagoon, thaw their butts and hurl giant fish.

episodes.name: Very Important Party
episodes.overview: Best friends battle against sibling teams in a competition to face the music, scream for ice cream and dazzle a bouncer.

episodes.name: Volcano a Go-Go
episodes.overview: Three teams race to crush their competition in epic challenges.

episodes.name: Can You Hear Me Now?
episodes.overview: Two teams of best friends battle cousins in a competition to learn how to speak snorkel, zip line through a coral mess and make the perfect lei.

episodes.name: Thunder on the Run
episodes.overview: "The Thundermans" cast members Kira, Addison and Jack team up with their super fans for a triathlon that includes a coconut milkshake windstorm and a kayak race.

episodes.name: Nicky, Ricky, Dicky & Run
episodes.overview: Nicky, Ricky, Dicky, and Dawn's Lizzy Greene, Casey Simpson, and Kyla-Drew Simmons team up with their superfans to party pupu piñata-style, send some gross spiders home, and break a Hawaiian curse.

episodes.name: Run Shakin'
episodes.overview: "Game Shakers" cast members Benjamin Flores Jr., Cree Cicchino and Thomas Kuc team up with their fans in a competition featuring a three-legged lobster race, a T-shirt disaster and coded Hawaiian messages.

episodes.overview: Stars of School of Rock take on stars of The Thundermans in a Hawaiian triathlon, a messed-up dress-up party, and a coconut windstorm before they run to the Final Suite.

episodes.overview: The stars of "Nicky, Ricky, Dicky and Dawn" team up with stars from "The Thundermans" to take on some mixed-up squid-words, a leaky volcano nose and a pool full of punch lines.

episodes.overview: The stars of "School of Rock" team up with their super fans to learn some birdie dances, fix some giant sandwiches and decode hidden messages.

episodes.name: Clash of the Nick Celebs
episodes.overview: The stars of "The Thundermans" take on the stars of "School of Rock" in a clash of Nickelodeon celebrities where they race through a Hawaiian spa, fix giant sandwiches and match mixed up jokes.

episodes.name: Game Shaking Up the Run
